text:
Hi Mike,I aware that we are focusing on collecting data’s from hospital to advise on data collection and provide data. I wanted to add additional potential resources of data includes:
Public health departments & institutes 
Local colleges/universities
Research organizations
Community volunteers
Consulting firms
Religion groups 
Community leaders 
I believe encouraging different group participation help perform this work consistently, neutrally and establish realistic expectations for what the gov can do to address community needs.
